## 7. Activity Diagram (Review Submission Flow)
This diagram maps the step-by-step activity flow for the core process: searching for a hospital and submitting a review, including page redirects.

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> SearchHospital: Patient accesses system
    SearchHospital --> ViewResults: Enters search criteria
    ViewResults --> ViewHospitalDetails: Selects a hospital
    
    ViewHospitalDetails --> [*]: Leaves page
    ViewHospitalDetails --> FillReviewForm: Clicks 'Write a Review'
    
    FillReviewForm --> AttachMedia: Provides ratings and feedback
    AttachMedia --> SubmitReview: Uploads optional proof
    
    SubmitReview --> ValidateData: System checks submission
    ValidateData --> FillReviewForm: Invalid data (shows errors)
    ValidateData --> ShowSuccessMsg: Valid data returns success
    
    ShowSuccessMsg --> RedirectToHospital: Redirect patient to Hospital Page
    RedirectToHospital --> ViewHospitalDetails: Page Reload
    
    ShowSuccessMsg --> PendingModeration: System adds review to queue
    
    PendingModeration --> AdminReview: Admin checks queue
    
    AdminReview --> Approved: Content meets guidelines
    AdminReview --> Rejected: Content violates policy
    
    Approved --> UpdateDatabase: Calculate new averages
    UpdateDatabase --> PublishReview: Add to public listing
    PublishReview --> [*]
    
    Rejected --> NotifyPatient: Send rejection email
    NotifyPatient --> [*]
```
